{
  "stem": "20581.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, our trucks, you know, we had 10 trucks and maybe with two, three sets of plates.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- we-- every time, we used to take off-- there were two plates.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, we took off one plate on one truck and one plate on the other truck.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, it was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We did-- the gasoline, we used to get from the army, in a depot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to get all these information.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we used to bring people from-- smuggle them-- bringing them over from Salzburg to [INAUDIBLE] to [INAUDIBLE] We used to drive-- I used to drive a truck.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Matter of fact, the American soldiers used to laugh at me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They used to say, you know, we were ready to shoot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We saw a truck without a driver.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, you imagine me, a little guy like this, driving a 10-wheeler, you know, with-- with 50 or 100 people in it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "OK, it was [? done. ?]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, nothing-- [? well, ?] in 1946, I-- I met my wife.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that's another story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Should I tell her the story?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened-- you know, like I told you, I was in-- I was in charge and-- I mean, in-- to bringing in the transports and [? so on. ?] So what happened one time, there was a transport coming in from Vienna to Salzburg.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And these people, they were little trouble makers, what we call them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were from Betar, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, with Jews, there's always something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's-- there-- there-- there two Jews in 20 different parties, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, everybody, so, the Betar wanted to take over.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
